high_descs: walk forwards a tiny bit, then take a right and walk to the garbage bin at the end of the room, then take a left and walk to the stove ahead
take the pot off of the back left burner
turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn right and face the kitchen sink
place the pot in the kitchen sink and clean it off, then take it back out
turn right and walk to the end of the room, then face the kitchen stove again on the left
place the burner back on the back left burner
anns.task_desc: place a clean pot on the back right burner of the stove

high_descs: Go to the stove in front of you.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Put the pot in the sink, turn on the water, and pick it up again.
Put the pot on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed pot on the stove.

high_descs: Pick up the dirty pot on the stove.
Take the dirty pot over to the sink on the right.
Wash the dirty pot in the sink
Take the clean pot back to the stove on the left.
Set the clean pot on the back left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on the stove.
